                            <comment id="256161" author="pjones" created="Wed, 9 Oct 2019 22:45:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.13&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="256154" author="gerrit" created="Wed, 9 Oct 2019 22:35:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (green@whamcloud.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/36351/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/36351/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12712&quot; title=&quot;sanity-pfl tests triggering &#8220;not SEL magic on SEL file&#8221;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12712&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12712&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; lod: fix warning message for non-SEL file&lt;br/&gt;
